videos.description: Alan Herndon gets a steal leading to an Louis Adams layup plus a foul on the other end.
videos.headline: Wyoming turns steal into and-1 layup

videos.description: Cody Martin gets a steal and passes it to his brother Caleb Martin who jams it home for Nevada.
videos.headline: Cody Martin sets up his brother Caleb for dunk

videos.description: Justin James shows off his range and hits a 3-pointer from way out for Wyoming.
videos.headline: James drains deep 3- pointer

videos.description: Cody Martin's nice pass leads to Lindsey Drew's up-and-under layup plus a foul for Nevada.
videos.headline: Drew makes tough and-1 layup

videos.description: Jordan Caroline drives and scores to tie the game at 74-74 for Wyoming, sending the game to overtime.
videos.headline: Caroline makes late layup to force OT

videos.description: Louis Adams drives and gets the shooters bounce to score for Wyoming in overtime.
videos.headline: Adams gets roll to score jumper

videos.description: Hayden Dalton hits a 3-pointer to stretch the lead for Wyoming in double overtime.
videos.headline: Dalton drills big 3-pointer
